# CoreConcepts [Typescript]

# Code [CodeConcept]

`Code` is a data type representing a fragment of generated output. It is the universal currency for code *de re* and templates.

  import { Data } from "effect";

  class Code extends Data.TaggedClass("Code")<{
    readonly content: string
  }> {}

